children.subject: Oops just saw the note. Sorry
This does not affect ESS advising, does it?

history.content:
Due to high demand, CS Advising will only offer drop-in advising between August 22 and September 7th, 2018. Our drop-in hours are 10am-12pm & 1-4pm in 379 and 315 Soda Hall. We will not be scheduling appointments through CalCentral during that time.

Additionally, EECS Advising will only offer drop-in advising between August 22 and September 7th, 2018. Our drop-in hours are 10am-12pm & 1-4pm in 205 Cory Hall. We will not be scheduling appointments through youcanbookme during that time. This does not apply to the Engineering Student Services advising office. 

As a friendly reminder, @6809
